body_html:
@ZacheryGuan Are you getting the warnings that were posted a bit above?

The TensorFlow library wasn't compiled to use SSE instructions, but these are available on your machine and could speed up CPU computations.

I think you could get rid of them if you build tensorflow on your machine first.
body:
@ZacheryGuan Are you getting the warnings that were posted a bit above?
```
The TensorFlow library wasn't compiled to use SSE instructions, but these are available on your machine and could speed up CPU computations.
```

I think you could get rid of them if you build tensorflow on your machine first.
